  • Constructor Details

    • Cliente

      public Cliente​(String cedula, String nombreCliente, int edad, char genero)
      Parameterized Constructor which loads a Cliente instance with its 4 basic attributes.
      Parameters:
      cedula - Person's ID (In Ecuador it is a "Cedula de Ciudadania")
      nombreCliente - Client's name
      edad - Client's age
      genero - Client's gender: Male or Female for this case it is a char, so it must be a 'M' or a 'F'
